title: Timmy Missions Destination Unknown | Winter Edition
description: Winter is Timmy's time to shine and he prides himself on surfing perfect uncrowded waves. He doesn't do it for the money, nor the fame, just pure love for riding waves. So, throw yourself in the shark tank or take a jet-ski on a slab hunting mission. Whatever it is make sure you watch this clip, it might make your day.
